He's tagged out !

48
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:28,000
Geez, they should read the flow of the game better.

49
00:03:30,900 --> 00:03:32,650
He's talking about baseball.

50
00:03:32,650 --> 00:03:34,460
So, do you want to go somewhere ?

51
00:03:34,460 --> 00:03:35,080
Hmm...

52
00:03:50,750 --> 00:03:52,200
Hi, Mr. Kunimi.

53
00:03:52,200 --> 00:03:54,150
Oh, Hikari. 
Are you looking for Hiro ?

54
00:03:54,650 --> 00:03:57,560
No, I'm just passing by.

55
00:03:57,560 --> 00:03:58,650
Oh, that's good.

56
00:03:59,670 --> 00:04:00,650
He's out ?

57
00:04:01,250 --> 00:04:06,380
Yeah. He's out again today, riding in a car with the president's daughter.

58
00:04:06,380 --> 00:04:07,250
The hospital ?

59
00:04:07,250 --> 00:04:12,550
She might be the manager, but she doesn't have to do so much for him.

60
00:04:13,550 --> 00:04:15,200
Isn't that a good thing ?

61
00:04:15,200 --> 00:04:16,200
Really ?

62
00:04:16,200 --> 00:04:17,330
It is.

63
00:04:18,790 --> 00:04:19,400
Oh ?

64
00:04:20,720 --> 00:04:21,350
Hm ?

65
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:24,980
Don't you have to go to work today ?

66
00:04:24,980 --> 00:04:27,970
Oh. You know, it's
 hot every day these days.

67
00:04:27,970 --> 00:04:30,950
I don't feel like going to work.

68
00:04:30,950 --> 00:04:33,970
What ? Then you're skipping ?

69
00:04:33,970 --> 00:04:35,720
Not.

70
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:40,200
Even for us adults,
there's summer vacation.

71
00:04:40,750 --> 00:04:41,830
I see.

72
00:04:44,650 --> 00:04:45,590
See you.

73
00:04:45,590 --> 00:04:46,370
Bye.

74
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:21,390
But I'm really glad.

75
00:05:22,080 --> 00:05:27,200
Well, as far as I'm concerned, 
I was hoping more had worn bikinis.

76
00:05:27,200 --> 00:05:32,650
If they're going to wear a one-pieces,
I wish they'd wear white see-through ones.

77
00:05:32,650 --> 00:05:35,040
I wish I had brought binoculars.

78
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:37,010
I'm talking about your leg injury.

79
00:05:38,300 --> 00:05:39,200
Oh.

80
00:05:40,100 --> 00:05:40,890
Check it out.

81
00:05:42,990 --> 00:05:44,630
That's the opposite leg.

82
00:05:45,670 --> 00:05:46,350
There.

83
00:05:53,730 --> 00:05:56,800
Anyway, there's no need to be impatient.

84
00:05:58,090 --> 00:06:02,190
Everything starts after summer break.

85
00:06:02,190 --> 00:06:03,010
That's right.

86
00:06:04,010 --> 00:06:07,550
The club room, the field, the coach.

87
00:06:07,550 --> 00:06:10,830
Getting new club members after the third years leave.

88
00:06:10,830 --> 00:06:14,340
We have so many things to do. These preparations will take up the entire fall.

89
00:06:14,340 --> 00:06:15,000
Right.

90
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:26,000
After the new first 
year students come in...

91
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:29,420
...we'll make a splash into the 
preliminary for the Koushien next year.

