Instead, we'll have a week 
long camp, starting tomorrow.

105
00:07:25,390 --> 00:07:27,120
What's wrong, Tachibana ?

106
00:07:27,120 --> 00:07:28,720
Um, nothing.

107
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:30,320
You have something 
else on your schedule ?

108
