And of course,
there shouldn't be.

110
00:07:33,650 --> 00:07:37,950
By all rights, we should be at the Koushien right now.

111
00:07:40,240 --> 00:07:43,650
Well, we'll let you rest up for today.

112
00:07:43,650 --> 00:07:44,500
That's all for now.

113
00:07:44,500 --> 00:07:45,600
Thank you.

